First record of the genus Echthronomas Forster, 1869 (Hymenoptera, Ichneumonidae, Campopleginae) for the fauna of UkraineAbstract The genus Echthronomas Forster, 1869 and two species, Echthronomas facialis (Thomson, 1887) and Echthronomas quadrinotata (Thomson, 1887), are recorded for the fauna of Ukraine for the first time. Descriptions and photographs of species are provided.